Texts.Chs: 跑来跑去做这么多任务，难道不累吗？
Texts.Eng: Does one not tire from running around doing so many tasks?

Texts.Chs: 叶族人将去世。叶族人按照自己的节奏做事。
Texts.Eng: Floran will passs. Floran does things at their own pace.

Texts.Chs: 用于组织和显示重要文件和照片。
Texts.Eng: For organizing and displaying important documents and photos.

Texts.Chs: 在这一片混乱中，这块软木木板的主人似乎挂上了一张爱人的照片，以示激励。
Texts.Eng: In the midst of all this clutter, the owner of this cork board seems to have hung up a photo of a loved one for motivation.

Texts.Chs: 这个人似乎在这里挂了一张爱人的照片。
Texts.Eng: It appears this person hangs a photo of a loved one on here.

Texts.Chs: 我，当我遇到他们时，我只是跨越了我的桥梁。
Texts.Eng: Me, I just cross my bridges when I come to 'em.

Texts.Chs: 拥有这块软木木板的人肯定是个爱管闲事的人。。。
Texts.Eng: The person who owns this cork board is certainly the busybody...

Texts.Chs: 哇，看着这家伙的日程表我就累了。
Texts.Eng: Woah, I feel tired just looking at this guy's schedule.
